In terminal: sudo nano /usr/share/applications/xxx.desktop

In text file:
[Desktop Entry]
Name=xxx
Type=Application
Exec=xxx (path to executable)
Terminal=false
Icon=xxx (path to icon (probably in the same map))
Comment=Any comment (yeah just add a comment)
NoDisplay=false
Categories=Development;IDE (Any category you want)
Name[en]=xxx (name shown in launcher)

